column4: Hi, in add/remove applications I see that the openJDK is installed I would like to install the sun jdk, but on removal it says 'one or more app depend on openJDK remove through package manager.' I start package manager but openJDK cannot be found...
I don't know how open jdk got installed
why can't I find openJdk in package manager?
Package names are always lowercase, search for openjdk
